RE Scott acre ranch preview Cc Do you have a package on this property or pictures Are there any improvements on the property house barn pens Thanks Scott Neal Original Message From Neal Scott mailtoScott NRONcom Sent Thursday October PM To Subject FW Scott acre ranch preview Original Message From Travis Wolf ENRON Sent Thursday October AM To Subject Scott acre ranch preview Hi Scott my name is Travis Wolf of Wolf Real Estate I wanted to let you know of a ranch I just listed for sale The ranch is acres min southeast of San Antonio miles from Stockdaletx it has miels of paved road frontage on hwy heavily wooded hunting ranch with large blackjack oaks game high fence on the back line the land has ponds of which are around acres plus in size the land is listed at per acre if your still in the market for a great hunting ranch or a great investment property contact me for more info Travis wolf Wolf Real Estate This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you

RE Webb Co ranch Cc What is the asking price on the Muela Creek ranch Also I am thinking about taking a trip to South Texas in the next few weeks Possibly Thursday Oct Saturday Oct Can someone show me the Rosita Ranch Thanks Scott Neal Original Message From FX ONeil mailto Sent Monday August PM To scott neal Subject Re Webb Co ranch Hi Scott yes unfortunetely that ranch sold several months ago I take it your still looking on that area Ill call you later this week so we can talk about some other properties that might work for you Feel free to call whenever you get a chance as well Talk to you soon FX ONeil Meek Ranch Sales

FW Welcome to TradebondscomOriginal Message From mailto Sent Tuesday September PM To Subject Welcome to Tradebondscom Dear scott neal We would like to take this moment to thank you for registering with Tradebondscom the premier fixed income online trading system Your User Name is sneal Your temporary Password is Please give the system three minutes to activate your settings then go to to login Enter your username and the temporary password listed above you can just cut and paste it Once youve logged in click on the link preferences located at the top of the page Reenter your username and temporary password then enter your new password in the new password field If you have any questions do not hesitate to contact us by phone or by email Welcome to Tradebondscom

FW muni portfolioOriginal Message From Shine David mailto Sent Tuesday November AM To scott neal Subject RE muni portfolio Scott Combined municipals short long attached Best regards David Original Message From scott neal mailto Sent Monday November PM To Shine David Subject RE muni portfolio Thank you Original Message From Shine David mailto Sent Monday November PM To scott neal Subject RE muni portfolio Scott I am glad you enjoyed the Rockets game I am preparing both reports short combined Ongoing you will receive a Quarterly Analysis on your municipals The first will come at the end of November with future reports Dec Mar June Sep Regards David Original Message From scott neal mailto Sent Sunday November PM To Subject muni portfolio David I was reviewing the page summary of the longer term muni bonds that I recently bought This summary is very helpful I would appreciate it if you could also provide me with the following a summary of the short term municpal bonds I bought about a month ago and a combined summary of all the municipal bonds I recently purchased Please call me should you have any questions at or Thank you Scott Neal Neal Combined Munis Finalxls

FW Reservation Confirmation Original Message From mailto Sent Monday November PM To Subject Reservation Confirmation Hello Scott Neal Thank you for booking your travel with us This email is being sent to confirm the travel plans you recently made with us We suggest you keep this message in case you need to contact us about this reservation Your Confirmation is Room Description DOUBLE BEDS NO SMOKINGCONTINENTAL BREAKFAST Room Rate in USD Arrival Date December Departure Date December of Adults of Rooms Estimated Total in USD Cancel Policy TO AVOID CHARGE CNCL BY PM HOTEL TIME Deposit Policy GUARANTEED FOR ONE NIGHT Hotel Name Best Western Market Center Hotel Address Market Center Boulevard Dallas TX US Property Phone Toll Free Reservations Reservation USCanada toll free Ireland toll free direct Italy toll free direct FAX Your reservation is complete and guaranteed however it may take hours before the hotels reservation system has been updated with this information therefore if you need to contact the hotel for any reason please wait until this hour period has passed Total amount stated above is an estimate based on the cost of the first nights stay The total indicated is a pretax total only If a rate change is indicated you may wish to contact the hotel regarding rate details during the course of your stay You may also wish to contact them regarding any supplemental room charges they may have not reported to us If no cancellation policy is stipulated above we recommend attempting cancellations at least hours prior to the reservation Cancellations may be made online by checking the Reservation Summary of your personal account at accountloginaspremotenh or by calling the number listed below during our regular business hours am pm EST Monday through Friday Cancellations requested by email are not guaranteed If you have questions or concerns please reply to this message at or go to faqhtml You can also call us at between am and pm EST
